Spent Christmas visiting Vietnam war memorials - or as they call it here, “The AMERICAN War”
Made a pretty good tunnel rat crawling through the Cu Chi Viet Cong tunnels. Not everyone is cut out for it (#7) but the booby traps, scorpions, heat & suffocation is a bit of a hazard. It’s all a stark reminder: War is ugly and brutal and affects generations long after the fighting stops. Cmon- it’s 2024, enough ✌🏼
